This episode is a conversation that has to happen everywhere -- with friends, family, and even within our tech community. JV is joined by Thunder E of Booredatwork to listen and share perspective on the current social climate that has dominated our feeds and our world.

S22
- 6.06” LTPS Display
- 50MP Main Sensor, 12MP Telephoto, 12MP Ultrawide 
- 3800mAh 
S22 Plus 
- 6.55” LTPS Display 
- 50MP Main Sensor, 12MP Telephoto, 12MP Ultrawide 
- 4600mAh
S22 Ultra 
- 6.81” LTPO Display 
- 108MP Main Sensor, 2 12MP Telephoto (3x zoom, 10x zoom), 12MP Ultrawide
- 5000mAh 

​​Finally, all three models are expected to feature an under-display selfie camera and the design will be a modified version of the S21 Series. What Samsung Lineup are you waiting for?
